column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,spp.ELODIERVFINAL,spp.ELODIERVFINALERR FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN sppParams AS spp ON spp.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   (p.u - p.g) > #  AND (p.g - p.r) BETWEEN # AND #  AND (p.u = p.g) BETWEEN # AND #  AND spp.LOGGWBG BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND spp.ELODIERVFINAL > #
